&lt;h3&gt;Level&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;Default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: windowtext;&quot;&gt;This apprenticeship standard is at Level 2. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Review date&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;Default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: windowtext;&quot;&gt;This apprenticeship standard will be reviewed after 3 years.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Progression&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apprentices may progress to Mechanical and Electrical Maritime Fitter at level 3.&lt;/p&gt;
